  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-934997cf-ab24-4dd6-aafe-ef443bf02b14\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-f90a586c-ed66-4c63-8ca0-16dc76969bb1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-58916114-7d0f-4e27-8813-328f49f0dd64\"><b>몸과 마음을 건강하게!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-67ff3ca7-3d22-4ef4-8ce4-3fb62804d10b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-7a252995-c889-4fc6-9a01-52b3bf25f797\"><b>안녕하세요, </b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-92fbfa7f-3bd1-4d84-9946-4e460df1075e\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-37abc167-a261-4ec1-96b2-d410881b0be8\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-934997cf-ab24-4dd6-aafe-ef443bf02b14\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-052c7dcb-0cbf-4f37-9aed-30d902879298\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"10\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_10.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e118ff8-616a-4a5a-bc42-d7b7585672b6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f5777ce-b654-40e6-8197-2dfdb3cea12b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1546badf-3868-49fb-bf66-e038469859f8\"><b>계속 피로감을 느끼고 자주 몸이 안좋은 것 같나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61c4b8a7-0cd8-4ff0-9364-c6f73721b2ce\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-85d9dcaf-a9d4-48ca-a5e8-a0a321fe6722\"><b>그럴때 </b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-38f974a6-800b-4f03-85a9-961cbe3ff983\"><b>경옥고</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0ad3070c-fd37-4c78-8c74-0a9fd08c97e1\"><b>를 처방 받아보세요!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-8e118ff8-616a-4a5a-bc42-d7b7585672b6\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-1dc2905a-7901-4974-ac42-43b5b1cd3708\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b0e4519e-df8d-4e13-b910-8fce6c3aa56b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b0e4519e-df8d-4e13-b910-8fce6c3aa56b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f77168e667b3b1b6.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2500\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2500\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f77168e667b3b1b6.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f77168e667b3b1b6.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-b0e4519e-df8d-4e13-b910-8fce6c3aa56b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-743c8ff5-daee-4af2-882b-905129a59110\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d45d95a3-477b-432c-9acd-5cc66938b009\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8bcdbd43-d5cd-46a7-95cf-93f4ae6ba0f3\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-743c8ff5-daee-4af2-882b-905129a59110\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d3af7fed-89b6-4a24-9129-3b8d67f1dd49\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83e0f3fb-f13f-42c6-b52f-a71797f9740c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1f723abe-02db-4b23-b107-ed23b15b1a29\"><b>경옥고란 무엇인가요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7268f72f-32a3-48bc-9841-939fc178646b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6c616ea4-fcca-4bfa-a1f0-5cbaf6c06d81\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-dfeb42f8-efdc-4046-a1b6-5644aa867b7f\">경옥고는 인삼, 생지황, 복령, 꿀 등의 귀한 약재를 오랜 시간 정성스럽게 달여 만든 고형 보약입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fb559920-b35a-48a5-93a3-5931c53c5954\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b465535a-0163-4b07-a805-6629bbd45e89\">이 네 가지 약재는 각각 다른 작용을 하며, 서로의 효능을 보완하여 몸을 기르고 정(精)을 채우는 역할을 합니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d8fd7a2-eae1-4802-bb04-7c8276f00062\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ac943c60-13f0-4ce8-ad0b-be9b07597465\">인삼(人蔘) : 기운을 보강하고 면역력을 높이는 대표적인 약재</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-874a1cde-f522-4eab-9b5c-d091d12fb0a3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-4a4e94da-d39d-41a6-838d-e35939d1d9d5\">생지황(生地黃) : 체내 열을 내려주고 혈액을 보충</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-636e47ed-6633-40fe-973f-489f0cba8443\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3562d889-7f67-4dac-b301-70dccca48628\">복령(茯苓) : 위장 기능을 개선하고 수분 대사를 돕는 약재</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2726e794-e237-45b2-a01d-cebdc64f2621\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-33ceec32-43cd-400e-aa8b-82a7606e94c8\">꿀(蜂蜜) : 다른 약재의 흡수를 도와주며 맛을 부드럽게 조절</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3444ac19-1581-4ba4-9a0f-301e534bd68c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c889c98f-3282-445e-815c-c1f028bb83aa\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d12a7e3-7ce0-4b66-9ef4-35ec5c0515cb\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3feb1ed7-9c96-4426-8d8f-43a2d30d53b8\">이 네 가지를 정해진 비율로 오래도록 고아내면, 진득하고 부드러운 고약 형태의 경옥고가 완성됩니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8892df46-4ca2-4e80-a892-13b5c18b26ae\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-dc97776c-8c41-4f4f-a8ab-a02a78dad79f\">현대에는 제조 과정을 위생적으로 관리하여 소포장 또는 환 형태로도 </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e69d1bf3-b524-4675-89d3-a9c85c46bab4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-61813c88-3a12-49db-8999-8a0963690610\">복용할 수 있도록 변형된 제품들도 많이 나와 있습니다.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-cf5d650c-f957-4f36-b9f9-04ebd62f6872\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7268f72f-32a3-48bc-9841-939fc178646b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3ce7b23b-2602-4719-8e40-83fcec32334e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:313px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3ce7b23b-2602-4719-8e40-83fcec32334e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f0f9a929154ce043.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f0f9a929154ce043.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f0f9a929154ce043.png\" data-width=\"313\" data-height=\"313\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-3ce7b23b-2602-4719-8e40-83fcec32334e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-64fb8635-8f8c-4b96-83b6-447d5003a2d8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-9a7a267b-08df-408b-9164-0b31d3c032d4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a602aa7-06ad-4cf2-aab4-c67a827e67d8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8262aa89-9529-4b83-b285-f725e077500a\"><b>경옥고, 어떤 분들께 좋을까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a32c851-8fba-4ea4-8546-a6b44e5eee5c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2bd6bc69-c78c-4def-85ec-85b8df576dc2\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9209c96a-0d61-4258-85d5-fb0cbc534cc1\">경옥고는 단순한 피로 회복을 넘어 기혈을 보하고 정을 보충하는 보약으로서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e7fe37b6-d523-47bb-bb4d-bad010a8cb6b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ad384ea2-2575-4156-84a7-fce5079f9543\">다양한 연령층과 건강 상태에 따라 활용할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-851fa5a7-9a84-4b99-9fdb-46e6b1cd67a3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ad93c174-aa08-4169-93fb-58dc18ed8e3b\">✔️ 기력이 부족하고 쉽게 지치는 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3896026-a85b-4b19-967c-1968b78d911f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-80af8709-b0de-4595-92c6-c2edbae58577\">✔️ 수면의 질이 낮고 아침에 개운하지 않은 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0cb0378a-3ba8-4d72-9051-30ba1b7b88b4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-144f18e2-b0f2-4e17-a41b-63d3493dc3d0\">✔️ 감기나 바이러스에 자주 노출되는 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61054c2a-628d-4cbc-966d-1b804f0584b8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e1c2cf12-3c21-4a2a-afbd-e54d3effa113\">✔️ 중장년층 이상의 체력 회복 및 노화 예방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-74811465-8382-48f1-b030-69a8b1794e0e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-082340f1-d1cc-4faa-8595-ae11a9078f1a\">✔️ 성장기 청소년의 면역력 및 집중력 보강</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b01e260a-cb59-4612-a534-bf9369b89381\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-7db1a5ad-8873-437f-98b7-841c08b0d60e\">✔️ 수술이나 질병 후 회복기 환자</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51d4f788-c785-4d51-a52b-5c5d500448ce\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e58e4caf-3565-4b7d-9077-df7c9190967b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d3f4cbb-7d8b-4775-a7b1-7e4be052ddef\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-53299dbf-2974-4113-afbb-2e786d6146e4\">특히 노년층이나 체력 소모가 많은 직장인, 학업 스트레스에 시달리는 학생들에게도 매우 효과적인 보약입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7a32c851-8fba-4ea4-8546-a6b44e5eee5c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a365863-964f-430e-aac0-6b3db8fba92e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit